{"comments":"Grid3D and GridScale — Multi-scale grid and axes helpers.\n\n## GridScale\n14 scales from Planck length (1.6×10^-35 m) to Parsec (3.1×10^16 m).\nCovers 51 orders of magnitude — from quantum minimum to galactic.\n\n## Grid3D\nRenders lines at regular intervals in the XZ plane (Y-up).\nMajor and minor grid lines have different colors/opacity for clarity.\n\n## Axes3D\nXYZ arrows with standard coloring: X=Red, Y=Green, Z=Blue (RGB = XYZ).\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[86,16],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Grid.purs","start":[86,3]},"title":"ScalePlanck"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Grid.purs","start":[87,3]},"title":"ScaleFemtometer"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Grid.purs","start":[88,3]},"title":"ScalePicometer"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[89,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Grid.purs","start":[89,3]},"title":"ScaleAngstrom"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Grid.purs","start":[90,3]},"title":"ScaleNanometer"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[91,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Grid.purs","start":[91,3]},"title":"ScaleMicrometer"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[92,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Scene3D/Grid.purs","start":[92,3]},"title":"ScaleMillimeter"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/sr